{"id": "art-1041", "label": "Art. 1041", "title": "Art. 1041", "slug": "art-1041", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_590577642\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2365\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_590577642\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 104<sup>1</sup></span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1065524964\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2364\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1065524964\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)<span class=SpellE>Ac&#355;iunile</span> dobândite cu\nînc&#259;lcarea prevederilor art. 103<sup>1</sup> <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\n</span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>104</span><span style='color:black'> trebuie\nînstr&#259;inate în termen de un an de la dobândire.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1571399710\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2363\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1571399710\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Dac&#259; valoarea nominal&#259; a propriilor <span\nclass=SpellE>ac&#355;iuni</span> dobândite de c&#259;tre societate în\nconformitate cu prevederile art. </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>104 alin.\n(1) lit. b)-d)</span><span style='color:black'>, fie direct, fie prin\nintermediul unei persoane <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionând</span> în nume\npropriu, dar în contul <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>, inclusiv\nvaloarea nominal&#259; a <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iunilor</span> proprii\nexistente deja în portofoliul <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>, <span\nclass=SpellE>dep&#259;&#351;e&#351;te</span> 10% din capitalul social subscris,\n<span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iunile</span> <span class=SpellE>dep&#259;&#351;ind</span>\nacest procent vor fi înstr&#259;inate în termen de 3 ani de la dobândire.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1836089858\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2362\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1836089858\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)În cazul în care <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iunile</span>\nnu sunt înstr&#259;inate în termenele prev&#259;zute la alin. (1) <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> (2), aceste <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iuni</span>\ntrebuie anulate, societatea fiind obligat&#259; s&#259; <span class=SpellE>î&#351;i</span>\nreduc&#259; în mod corespunz&#259;tor capitalul social subscris.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}